item.title: Prayer bpn12385 in Namibia
item.description: Khoeë hâ, ≠Khôana //khaebe //khae? Elob ose Mî: Ab Eloba gare he re //îb a Elo, Hoan a //îb !ga tsî hoan nî //îb Mî-mâisa di //oa-//oa! (Source category: Khoekhoegowab: MÂ XO-/KHAS) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 12385)
